channel.title: Ok this is seriusoly retarded
channel.description: This is how it happened. I was walking to class when the teacher shut the door in my face my nose started bleeding then she opened the door back up the exact time I said baise (Which is fuck in french by the way) and she yelled at me and sent me to the office. So I'm at the office and they asked why am I here (My nose is still bleeding) and I said I got sent here because I swore and then she asked what did you say; and I said that I said fuck and then the Principal heard me and said your suspened young man and I'm calling your mother. So my Mother comes and asked why they wanted her and they said because I said fuck and she said Ok so what he said fuck and they asked me to come over and they asked why I was so pale and I said my nose has been bleeding for the past hour and your complaining because I said fuck... I still got suspened.
